Yuval is a graduate of the Holon Institute of Technology, where he studied visual communication design specializing in interactive design.

His passion is user experience and interfaces, with a pixel-perfect attitude. He has worked  with several startups including 5min, later purchased by AOL. He discovered Bitcoin at 2011, and in 2013 joined [[Ron|Ron_Gross]] in founding [[Bitblu]] as the Chief Product Officer.

